      %br
      See the results of your feedback visualised in
      %a{ :href => "/results", :title => "Thanks for Helping us out!"}
        pretty chart form.

    %div.col-md-6
      %h4
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-eye-open
        Looking for goodies to play with?
      An online smart-map for orientation when out-and-about is available
